headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Bircroft Insurance Services
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of London, UK-based Bircroft Insurance Services (Bircroft). Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
